From Lois Christiansen Subject Re Homosexuality issues in Christianity In article M wrote In article Lois Christiansen writes You might visit some congregations of Christians who happen to be homosexuals that are spirit filled believers not MCC'rs before you go lumping us all together with Troy Gee I think there are some real criminals robbers muderers drug addicts who appear to be fun loving caring people So what's your point Is it just because the people are nice I didn't say to visit some nice I said visit some congregations of filled Praise the Lord that we are all members of the same Let us agree to God Bless You and See you in Heaven Loisc